{"route":"/docs/reference/layout/box/","title":"Box","description":"Documentation for the `box` function.","part":null,"outline":[{"id":"summary","name":"概要","children":[]},{"id":"例","name":"例","children":[]},{"id":"parameters","name":"引数","children":[{"id":"parameters-width","name":"width","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-height","name":"height","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-baseline","name":"baseline","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-fill","name":"fill","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-stroke","name":"stroke","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-radius","name":"radius","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-inset","name":"inset","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-outset","name":"outset","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-clip","name":"clip","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-body","name":"body","children":[]}]}],"body":{"kind":"func","content":{"path":[],"name":"box","title":"Box","keywords":[],"oneliner":"コンテンツの大きさを持つインラインレベルのコンテナ。","element":true,"contextual":false,"deprecation":null,"details":"<p>コンテンツの大きさを持つインラインレベルのコンテナ。</p>\n<p>インライン数式、テキスト、ボックスを除く全ての要素はブロックレベルであり、<a href=\"/docs/reference/model/par/\">段落</a>の中に含めることはできません。\nbox関数を用いることで、そのような要素を段落にまとめることができます。\nボックスはデフォルトで、受け取ったコンテンツに合わせた大きさになりますが、明示的に大きさを指定することもできます。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例\">例</h2>\n<div class=\"previewed-code\"><pre><code>Refer to the docs\n<span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">box</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>\n  height<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">9pt</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"typ-func\">image</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;docs.svg&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n<span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\nfor more information.\n</code></pre><div class=\"preview\"><img src=\"/docs/assets/781f4d033bb6c64f8ed6689f7e8cf029.png\" alt=\"Preview\"></div></div>","example":null,"self":false,"params":[{"name":"width","details":"<p>ボックスの幅。</p>\n<p>ボックスは以下の例で示すように、<a href=\"/docs/reference/layout/fraction/\">比率</a>を用いて幅を指定できます。</p>\n<p><em>注意:</em> 現在、パラグラフ内で比率指定が可能なのはボックスおよびその幅のみです。\n比率で指定した大きさを持つ画像や図形などは今後サポートされる可能性があります。</p>","example":"<div class=\"previewed-code\"><pre><code>Line in <span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">box</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>width<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">1fr</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span> <span class=\"typ-func\">line</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>length<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">100%</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span> between.\n</code></pre><div class=\"preview\"><img src=\"/docs/assets/77326ba2a90f710f23d720fa9d9484d0.png\" alt=\"Preview\"></div></div>","types":["auto","relative","fraction"],"strings":[],"default":"<code><span class=\"typ-key\">auto</span></code>","positional":false,"named":true,"required":false,"variadic":false,"settable":true},{"name":"height","details":"<p>ボックスの高さ。</p>","example":null,"types":["auto","relative"],"strings":[],"default":"<code><span class=\"typ-key\">auto</span></code>","positional":false,"named":true,"required":false,"variadic":false,"settable":true},{"name":"baseline","details":"<p>ボックスのベースラインをシフトさせる量。</p>","example":"<div class=\"previewed-code\"><pre><code>Image: <span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">box</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>baseline<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">40%</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span> <span class=\"typ-func\">image</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;tiger.jpg&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span> width<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">2cm</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>.\n</code></pre><div class=\"preview\"><img src=\"/docs/assets/8cd6665dc2d94162a88dbe58873dee11.png\" alt=\"Preview\"></div></div>","types":["relativ